  "commit_message": "fix(server): prevent Electron beforeunload prompt from hanging navigation (#33981)\n\n* fix(server): prevent Electron beforeunload prompt from hanging navigation\n\nPages that register a beforeunload handler requesting a confirmation\nprompt (window.onbeforeunload returning a string or setting\nevent.returnValue) caused the Electron browser to hang and eventually\nfail navigation with a pageLoadTimeout. Electron surfaces these prompts\nvia the webContents 'will-prevent-unload' event, which Cypress never",
